            <sentence id="3.2">Steps to Reproduce:</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.3">1 Right click the Navigation Toolbar and hit customize.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.4">2 Show: "Icons and Text".</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.5">3 Look at the buttons already on the Toolbar and the ones in the Customize menu.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Actual Results:  
A few of the button text is off-center, with the Stop text being the most noticable.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
